column5: Please don't. Suicide might be a seemingly easy thing to do but many don't know that this will ultimately cause you to lose. I've been there, I realize now that I can't go through with it because it'll hurt my loved ones. In the moments of hopelessnes I thought they could be happy but after I tried my grandfather cried for the fist time. I didn't know that his mother committed suicide, I never wanted to hurt him as much as I did. And you will realise that you are stronger than you might think. When you hang on you will find a reason and you will fight for it. ❤️
Your Mom will love you forever and I am just a stranger on the internet but I'm here for you ❤️ It might sound silly but I care about you and so do many others
